{"tid":492992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又海報挑機？中國隊今發布東亞賽宣傳海報：「在亞洲我們不懼怕任何對手」","createTime":"2017-12-08T05:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T06:13:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c0e67eba21e1a2cdd21bcd836ce8847444a89c","tid":492992,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171208/s00006/0d2e3d24e252751b1422749ab417abb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171208%2Fs00006%2F0d2e3d24e252751b1422749ab417abb4.jpg&h=c9aeb569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年東亞足球錦標賽將於今日起至16日在日本東京舉行，4支決賽周球隊包括中國、日本、韓國和朝鮮。中國隊今日在微博發放了一張出戰該項賽事的宣傳海報，除了畫出男女子國足的卡通角色，還引用國足教練納比此前所言：「在亞洲我們不懼怕任何對手」作標語。<br />\n<br />\n兩年一度的東亞錦標賽今年為第7屆，今午3時10分打頭陣為女子足球，由中國女足對朝鮮女足，至於男子國足，首場賽事就將於明午3時30分，在東京味之素球場迎戰韓國。12日和16日分別對日本和朝鮮。<br />\n<br />\n國足以至中超球隊，近年都不時在賽前的宣傳海報加上霸氣標語，如2015年的世界盃亞洲區第2圈外圍賽，中國與香港同組，中國足協曾設計「不輕視任何對手」系列的海報，當中對港隊的海報還寫上：「這支球隊的人，有黑皮膚，有黃皮膚，有白皮膚，這麼有層次的球隊，得防着點！」，結果引起本地球迷不滿有輕視港足和有種族歧視之嫌。香港足總隨即在網上發放一款類似格式的海報「回應」，用廣東話寫上「唔好比（畀）人睇死」、「我哋呢支球隊，有黑皮膚，有黃皮膚，有白皮膚。目標都係要為香港出一口氣，你係香港人點都要撐！」足總相關同事因而獲不少本地球迷讚賞反應夠快。最終當年9月和11月，兩戰中國均踢成0：0。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171208/s00006/1512709655697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171208%2Fs00006%2F1512709655697&d=jDd7n1Vz9sOp%2FOQjG5Txkdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=fbf8e5d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171208%2Fs00006%2F1512709655697&h=f75f1b5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171208/s00006/1512709655697</a>"},{"pid":"0e0a757b3007d5de49e1d20ab25efaa856a76fe4","tid":492992,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b83a4b9e3cd5288f4acf6d4f6c5ffe7b6d4cbf3","tid":492992,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:45:50.000Z","msg":"返大陸啦仆街"},{"pid":"3add08dea556ffa2dec7af79733701bea6066f41","tid":492992,"uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:51:48.000Z","msg":"在<span style=\"color: red;\">亞洲電視</span>我們不懼怕任何對手"},{"pid":"f54da43a2104ba5088a2b4e27c4c91bfc555f7f8","tid":492992,"uid":32722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"係唔懼怕，輸咋麻"},{"pid":"c07128a86147f44d8e0fab0e7b2061f263fb7049","tid":492992,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"每次呢啲比賽，十次買強国對家，起碼有七次收錢"},{"pid":"371387b87eb972df273b4da0125eea9572c04757","tid":492992,"uid":18566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:56:46.000Z","msg":"好似網上行d海報"},{"pid":"de1f79b4eb000d7225f9ede2697f5f7deff0d7a1","tid":492992,"uid":92614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"講到一出亞洲就好驚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af14e9c13b73ab580b853eb91bd39b56a78bafd2","tid":492992,"uid":20609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"都輸慣啦。仲怕咩呢"},{"pid":"7c4d0a2752a4c2b75ac53a91e1bcb6c846cb328a","tid":492992,"uid":134438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:01:14.000Z","msg":"係咪一出左亞洲就淆撚晒底？"},{"pid":"e16a94a22c18d8c93551c7b139734f2c9e58e451","tid":492992,"uid":31354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:01:14.000Z","msg":"你班垃圾都唔怕輸<br />\n有咩所謂，都輸慣"},{"pid":"86647e6161422454b1d173ea2fed4755f2e4d041","tid":492992,"uid":14719,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"殘體注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"htt